--- title: 2020 (Re)Insurer Stock Price Performance author: '' date: '2021-01-31' slug: 2020-re-insurer-stock-price-performance categories: [] tags: - insurance - stocks draft: false ---

In this post, we review the 2020 stock price returns for US property and casualty (re)insurers.

The top 5 performing stocks are shown in the graph below. All five of the stocks more than doubled the S&P500 return. KNSL and PLMR were both in the top 5 performing stocks in 2019.

If we focus on the largest five P&C stocks (by market cap). Only PGR outperformed the S&P500 with the other four stocks significantly underperforming.

The table below summarizes the 2020 performance for all US listed P&C and Life (re)insurer stocks.
